reviewText: Show is great germanys answer to star trek. Soundtrack is krarfwekkrarfwek meets Duke Ellington. Had to buy the cd too.
Lots of fun. Somewhat in the spirit of the early '50s West German-made Flash Gordon series. Engrossing and unusual. Highly recommended.

Is there a version available that would play in the us?
I have seen this as a kid in Germany, German version of star track, unfortunately they made only a few, by the way it's older than star track
